text: Dolly-Rose Campbell (born 12 April 1987) is an English actress, known for her portrayal of Gemma Winter on the ITV soap opera Coronation Street, a role she has played since October 2014. ==Other websites== * Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:English television actors Category:Bisexual people Category:English LGBT people Category:LGBT actors Category:Actors from Greater Manchester Category:People from Salford
